The lovely Anya. A sexy student who is struggling to make ends meet. When she moves in with her school friend Bree to share the rent, Bree begins to meet up with a sexy European guy who has money, looks and loves a younger woman. When Bree tells Anya that her sugar daddy would love to meet up with her, at first she is a little apprehensive, but she knows that if she wants her money troubles gone, she has to take this opportunity. All she needs to do is be a good little girl and grant his every wish
